PuzzleGame.App

类 View

  • java.lang.Object
    • PuzzleGame.App.View
  • 直接已知子类:
    BeginView, ChooseView, FinishView, GameView

    public abstract class View
extends java.lang.Object
    View class which holds pane. Pane is the view players see and interact with.
    作者:
    Group 10 - Heather Xiong - 20722114 2022/5/14
    Function:
    This is the parent for every view created. View life cycle methods:, 1. onLaunch(): launch the components in the view, onFinish(), 2. onEnter(), onLeave(), 3. onStart():start the game, onUpdate(): update the view, adding some function like key or mouse detection, onStop()
